{"tid":1575168,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"被大陸拖累 穆迪投資下調香港評級","createTime":"2019-09-16T17:24:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T21:41:48.000Z","uid":263822,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1f95ff023a8322017f9aadb6a763f7002e5bd208","tid":1575168,"uid":263822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T17:24:42.000Z","msg":"好似冇咩人講？ <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>被大陸拖累</strong></span>[/size=4] 穆迪削香港評級至Aa2<br />\n<br />\n節錄 TLDR<br />\n<br />\nThe institutional features which grant Hong Kong a degree of political and economic autonomy &mdash; together with its intrinsic credit strengths &mdash; account for [size=5]<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Hong Kong's higher rating when compared with China</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n... <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>Closer linkages with China</ins></strong></span></span> in Hong Kong's institutional framework and policymaking <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins>would lead to an erosion</ins></strong> in the currently very high strength of Hong Kong's governing and judicial institutions, policy effectiveness and competitive advantage over large cities in the mainland and other international trade or financial hubs.</span></span><br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.moodys.com/research/Moodys-changes-outlook-on-Hong-Kongs-Aa2-rating-to-negative--PR_409149\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moodys.com%2Fresearch%2FMoodys-changes-outlook-on-Hong-Kongs-Aa2-rating-to-negative--PR_409149&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rSWBhM8hN5wqk8YifI4Fu34%3D&h=db6d7d69\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.moodys.com/research/Moodys-changes-outlook-on-Hong-Kongs-Aa2-rating-to-negative--PR_409149</a><br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講基於香港自治下嘅政制、司法同競爭力都比大陸優勝，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>所以香港投資評級一直都<ins>比大陸高</ins></strong></span></span>。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>而瀨共係會直接收窄呢個投資評級差距</strong></span></span>，即係等同出賣香港現時國際金融中心地位。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>瀨共嘅人係直接損害緊香港未來嘅經濟，不得好死</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38014343e42707f4c652c9477e5602823a0e9098","tid":1575168,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T17:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvsTHEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvsTHEi.jpg&h=e8bfe3ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">星期三有大綱睇</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\n<br />\nsuck 4.0 將會基於 hkmap.live 行動  <br />\n麻煩力推呢個livemap <br />\n對各位日後行動都非常大幫助<br />\n<br />\n請各位必須係 9月22日當日12點30分留意channel / 連登 / IG 最新消息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n TG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rSWBhM8hN5wqk8YifI4Fu34%3D&h=007b2bf3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://instagram.com/suck.withyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fsuck.withyou&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rSWBhM8hN5wqk8YifI4Fu34%3D&h=d8f0d69b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/suck.withyou</a></span>"},{"pid":"1232a360af5ba45a11f6beed5e04c92c082a6e31","tid":1575168,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T17:26:38.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"a2720a74511029e63e6226e49b976f1f2a494e33","tid":1575168,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc